Takealot has teamed up with Samsung to back the Springboks to win the 2019 Rugby World Cup. Takealot is giving customers an excellent promotional offer: Buy a selected Samsung TV, and Takealot will give you your money back in full if the Springboks win the Rugby World Cup. By participating in this promotion, users agree to all the promotional rules – set out in the full terms and conditions. More details on the promotion are available below. The Samsung TVs – which have been discounted and that form part of the promotion – are shown below. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-318945" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/TV-2.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/TV-2.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/TV-2-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/TV-2-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-318947" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/TV-3.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/TV-3.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/TV-3-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/TV-3-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-318941" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/TV.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/TV.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/TV-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/TV-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85v